name: Zachary Simmons
review: A Christ-honoring, truth-teaching, people-loving church. Our family has been blessed every time we've worshiped here while traveling at the beach. You should visit!

name: John Pflug
review: Enjoyed the worship and the people. Solid Biblical preaching.

name: Nathan Magnusen
review: Very Christ centered and welcoming church! The folks there really made us feel at home!

name: Bradley Fainra
review: Very pleasant, relaxed and friendly church! Preached the Gospel.
